Aku akan bicara dengan Ibu.

264
00:23:18,125 --> 00:23:19,285
Dia harus mengerti.

265
00:23:20,291 --> 00:23:21,881
Sial! Mereka segera tiba.

266
00:23:25,750 --> 00:23:27,040
Bagaimana perasaanmu?

267
00:23:31,375 --> 00:23:32,995
Aku ingin muntah.

268
00:23:35,833 --> 00:23:37,463
Nanti kutelepon.

269
00:23:39,541 --> 00:23:40,671
Kau akan hebat.

270
00:23:43,041 --> 00:23:44,081
Kau berani.

271
00:24:05,291 --> 00:24:07,671
Terima kasih karena tak meninggalkanku.

272
00:24:16,916 --> 00:24:18,626
Hai. Kupikir…

273
00:24:18,708 --> 00:24:20,958
Aku ingin kita berduaan sebentar.

274
00:24:28,958 --> 00:24:29,788
Apa kabar?

275
00:24:33,458 --> 00:24:34,288
Salam kenal.

276
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:37,920
Yang Mulia.

277
00:24:40,291 --> 00:24:41,131
