Mau mengunjungiku di New York?

352
00:32:28,875 --> 00:32:29,705
Halo?

353
00:32:33,958 --> 00:32:34,788
Felice?

354
00:32:45,625 --> 00:32:49,325
- Yang mana kamar Wilhelm?
