368
00:33:44,708 --> 00:33:47,418
Ponselnya jatuh,
dan kurasa kameranya rusak.

369
00:33:48,416 --> 00:33:49,416
Di sini juga.

370
00:33:50,625 --> 00:33:52,625
Sama persis di setiap foto.

371
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:19,080
Hei!

372
00:34:26,083 --> 00:34:27,293
Aku memercayaimu.

373
00:34:30,083 --> 00:34:31,333
Apa maksudmu?

374
00:34:32,416 --> 00:34:33,536
Aku sangat percaya.

375
00:34:34,708 --> 00:34:35,708
Kenapa?

376
00:34:54,458 --> 00:34:55,538
Maafkan aku.

377
00:34:56,375 --> 00:34:57,285
