383
00:35:34,666 --> 00:35:36,626
Kau bukan lagi keluargaku.

384
00:35:54,791 --> 00:35:55,631
Hai, Sayang.

385
00:35:56,458 --> 00:35:57,668
Ibu, itu August.

386
00:35:58,125 --> 00:35:59,415
August pelakunya.

