00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:04,380
- Aku tahu.
- Apa maksudnya?

388
00:36:06,333 --> 00:36:07,713
Sejak kapan?

389
00:36:09,166 --> 00:36:10,456
Sudah beberapa hari.

390
00:36:12,041 --> 00:36:13,461
- Bagaimana?
- Wille…

391
00:36:13,541 --> 00:36:16,251
