394
00:36:20,791 --> 00:36:24,251
Kita bilang kau tak ada di video,
itu cerita yang dipakai.

395
00:36:24,333 --> 00:36:25,963
Dia harus dihukum, 'kan?

396
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:28,540
Dia menghancurkan hidupku!

397
00:36:29,083 --> 00:36:30,923
